description:
I took my cat Luke with me on my trip from the US to the Philippines on June 2021. In this video, I am sharing what I had to complete to approve his travel.

https://www.bringfido.com/travel/international/philippines/
https://www.philippineconsulatela.org/consular-services-2/notar1als/related-services/importation-of-pets-to-the-philippines
https://www.intercommerce.com.ph/registrationbai.asp
